                                        <p class="has-medium-font-size">Quadriceps</p>
                                        <p class="has-small-font-size"><p><span data-sheets-root="\&quot;1\&quot;" data-sheets-value="\&quot;{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Muscles" data-sheets-userformat="\&quot;{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;11&quot;:3,&quot;12&quot;:0}\&quot;">Muscles located at the front portion of your upper legs, below your pelvis and above your knees. Consists of four parts. </span></p></p>
